## 🔥 **Win / Lose**

```gdscript id="r6lmpb"
func win_game():
	$UI/ResultText.text = "Nice Move"
	get_tree().paused = true

func lose_game():
	$UI/ResultText.text = "Nice Try"
	get_tree().paused = true
```

